              <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
            <h3 class="feat-title">Security</h3>
            <p class="feat-desc">语义级 Prompt 注入扫描。检测并拦截攻击，保护 Agent 运行安全。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feat-item">
            <svg class="feat-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M18 8a3 3 0 010 6"/>
              <path d="M10 8H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h4l5 4V4l-5 4z"/>
              <path d="M22 5a9 9 0 010 14"/>
            </svg>
            <h3 class="feat-title">Channels</h3>
            <p class="feat-desc">将 Agent 接入 Telegram，支持完整媒体处理与群组上下文。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feat-item">
            <svg class="feat-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
